DEPLOYMENT CHECKLIST (run in order)
════════════════════════════════════════

1. dotnet build MaemoCompliance.sln — 0 errors
2. dotnet test MaemoCompliance.UnitTests — all pass
3. dotnet test MaemoCompliance.IntegrationTests — all pass
4. npm run build --configuration production — 0 errors
5. git push origin main
6. GitHub Actions: all jobs green
7. On server: git pull origin main
8. Run migrations if new ones exist
9. docker compose -f docker-compose.prod.yml up -d
10. curl https://api.maemo-compliance.co.za/health/live
    → {"status":"Healthy"}
11. curl -sI https://maemo-compliance.co.za
    → HTTP/2 200
